# {{context|science|lang=en}} A system of units formerly used in physics (now replaced by the [[SI]] system), in which the basic units of length, mass and time were respectively [[centimeter]], [[gram]], and [[second]].  Abbreviated as [[cgs]] or [[CGS]].

